text: The Miss Minnesota's Outstanding Teen competition is the pageant that selects the representative for the U.S. state of Minnesota in the Miss America's Outstanding Teen pageant. Bella Grill of Lino Lakes was crowned Miss Minnesota's Outstanding Teen on March 14, 2020 at Central Lakes College in Brainerd, Minnesota. She will compete for the title of Miss America's Outstanding Teen 2021 at the Linda Chapin Theater in the Orange County Convention Center on August 8th, 2020 in Orlando, Florida. == Results summary == The results of Miss Minnesota's Outstanding Teen as they participated in the national Miss America's Outstanding Teen competition.
